Apache Cassandra is an Open-source NoSQL distributed database
A managed Apache Cassandra compatible database service
serverless, scalable, highly available, fully managed by AWS
Automatically scale tabless up/down based on traffic
tables are replicated 3 times across multiple AZ
using the Cassandra Query Language (CQL)
Single-digit millisecond latency at any scale, 1000s requests per second
capacity: on-demand mode or provisioned with auto-scaling
encryption: PITR up to 35 days
use cases: Store IoT devices info, time-series data
